\c 26
\s Iqhinga lokubulala uJesu
\p
\v 1 Kwasekusithi uJesu eseqedile wonke lamazwi, wathi kubafundi bakhe:
\v 2 Liyazi ukuthi emva kwensuku ezimbili kuzakuba liphasika, leNdodana yomuntu izanikelwa ukuze ibethelwe\x + Mark. 14.1,2. Luka 22.1,2. Joha. 11.55; 13.1.\x*.
\v 3 Kwasekubuthana abapristi abakhulu lababhali labadala babantu\x + Joha. 11.47. Hlab. 2.2. Seb. 4.25-27.\x* egumeni lompristi omkhulu\x + Isam. 11.2.26.58,69. Mark. 14.54; 15.16. Luka 11.21; 22.55. Joha. 18.15. Mark. 14.66.\x* othiwa nguKayafasi\x + 26.57. Luka 3.2. Joha. 11.49; 18.13,14,24,28. Seb. 4.6.\x*,
\v 4 basebecebisana ukuthi bambambe uJesu ngobuqili ba\add m\add*bulale.
\v 5 Kodwa bathi: Kungabi ngomkhosi, ukuthi kungabi khona isiphithiphithi ebantwini\x + 27.24.\x*.
\s UJesu ugcotshwa eBethani
\p
\v 6 Kwathi uJesu\x + Mark. 14.3-9. Joha. 12.1-8. Luka 7.36-50.\x* eseBethani endlini kaSimoni umlephero\x + 21.17.\x*,
\v 7 kwafika kuye owesifazana ephethe umfuma \w we-alibasta\w** ulamagcobo aligugu elikhulu\x + Mark. 14.3. Luka 7.37.\x*, wase\add wu\add*thululela ekhanda lakhe ehlezi ekudleni\x + Joha. 12.3. Luka 7.38.\x*.
\v 8 Kodwa abafundi bebona \add lokhu\add* bathukuthela, bathi: Ngokwani ukumotsha lokhu\x + Joha. 12.4.\x*?
\v 9 Ngoba la amagcobo angathengiswa ngokunengi, besekunikwa abayanga\x + Mark. 14.5. Joha. 12.5.\x*.
\v 10 Kodwa uJesu ekwazi wathi kubo: Limhluphelani owesifazana? Ngoba wenzile umsebenzi omuhle kimi;
\v 11 ngoba abayanga lihlala lilabo\x + Dute. 15.11.\x*, kodwa mina kalihlali lilami\x + Joha. 13.33.\x*.
\v 12 Ngoba ngokuthululela la amagcobo emzimbeni wami, u\add kw\add*enzele umngcwabo wami\x + Joha. 19.40. Mark. 14.8. Joha. 12.7. Gen. 50.2.\x*.
\v 13 Ngiqinisile ngithi kini: Loba ngaphi emhlabeni wonke lapho okuzatshunyayelwa khona lelivangeli, lalokho akwenzileyo kuzakhulunywa ngakho, kube yisikhumbuzo ngaye\x + Seb. 10.4.\x*.
\s Umvuzo wokunikela uJesu
\p
\v 14 Omunye wabalitshumi lambili\x + Mark. 14.10,11. Luka 22.3-6. Joha. 13.2,27,30.\x*, othiwa nguJudasi Iskariyothi\x + 10.4.26. 25,47. 27.3.\x*, wasesiya kubapristi abakhulu,
\v 15 wathi: Livuma ukunginikani, mina-ke ngizamnikela kini? Basebevumelana laye\x + Mark. 14.11. Luka 22.5, Ezra 8.25. Jer. 32.9.\x* ngenhlamvu zesiliva ezingamatshumi amathathu\x + Eks. 21.32.\x*.
\v 16 Njalo kusukela lapho wadinga ithuba elihle lokumnikela.
\s Ukumiswa kwesidlo esingcwele
\p
\v 17 Kwathi\x + Mark. 14.12-16. Luka 22.7-13.\x* ngolokuqala lwesinkwa esingelamvubelo abafundi beza kuJesu\x + Eks. 12.6,18.\x*, besithi kuye: Uthanda ukuthi sikulungisele ngaphi ukuthi udle iphasika?
\v 18 Wasesithi: Hambani liye emzini kumuntu othile\x + Mark. 14.13. Luka 22.10.\x*, lithi kuye: UMfundisi uthi\x + Joha. 11.28. Joha. 3.10.\x*: Isikhathi sami sesiseduze\x + Joha. 7.6,8. Joha. 7.30; 8.20.\x*; ngizakwenza iphasika kwakho kanye labafundi bami\x + Seb. 18.21. Heb. 11.28.\x*.
\v 19 Benza-ke abafundi njengoba uJesu ebalayile, basebelungisa iphasika\x + 27.10.\x*.
\v 20 Kwathi sekuhlwile\x + Mark. 14.17-21.\x* wayehlezi labalitshumi lambili\x + Luka 22.14.\x*.
\v 21 Bathi besidla wathi: Ngiqinisile ngithi kini: Omunye wenu uzanginikela\x + Joha. 13.21.\x*.
\v 22 Basebedabuka kakhulu baqala ukuthi kuye ngamunye wabo: Nkosi, ayisimi, akunjalo yini\x + Luka 3.8. Luka 22.23. Joha. 13.22.\x*?
\v 23 Wasephendula wathi: Ofaka isandla \add sakhe\add* kanye lami emganwini, nguye ozanginikela\x + Joha. 13.18.\x*.
\v 24 Sibili iNdodana yomuntu\x + Luka 22.22.\x* ihamba, njengokulotshiweyo ngayo\x + Mark. 9.12. Mat. 26.54,56. Luka 24.25,26,27,46. Seb. 17.2,3; 26.22,23. 1 Kor. 15.3. 1 Pet. 1.11.\x*; kodwa maye kulowomuntu iNdodana yomuntu enikelwa nguye\x + 18.7.\x*\x + Mark. 9.12. Mat. 26.54,56. Luka 24.25,26,27,46. Seb. 17.2,3; 26.22,23. 1 Kor. 15.3. 1 Pet. 1.11.\x*! Bekungakuhle kuye aluba lowomuntu wayengazalwanga\x + Joha. 17.12.\x*.
\v 25 Wasephendula uJudasi owamnikelayo wathi: \w Rabi\w**, ayisimi, akunjalo yini\x + Joha. 13.26.\x*? Wathi kuye: Utshilo wena\x + 26.64. 27.11.\x*.
