\v 26 Kwathi besidla, uJesu wathatha isinkwa\x + Mark. 14.22-25. Luka 22.19,20. 1 Kor. 11.23-25.\x*, wase\add si\add*busisa, wa\add si\add*hlephula wabanika abafundi, wathi: Thathani, lidle; lokhu kungumzimba wami\x + 1 Kor. 10.16.\x*.
\v 27 Wasethatha inkezo, wabonga, wabanika\x + 26.26.\x*, esithi: Nathani lonke kuyo;
\v 28 ngoba lokhu\x + 1 Kor. 10.16.\x* kuligazi lami\x + Eks. 24.8.\x*, elesivumelwano esitsha\x + Jer. 31.31.\x*, elichithelwa abanengi\x + 20.28.\x* kukho ukuthethelelwa kwezono\x + Mark. 1.4. Luka 3.3. Seb. 2.38. Levi 17.11. Heb. 9.22.\x*.
\v 29 Kodwa ngithi kini: Kusukela khathesi kangiyikunatha okwalesisithelo sevini, kuze \add kufike\add* lolosuku lapho ngizasinatha lani sisitsha\x + Luka 22.18.\x* embusweni kaBaba\x + 13.43. Luka 22.30.\x*.
\v 30 Kwathi sebehlabele ingoma\f + \fk ingoma: \ft kumbe, \fq isihlabelelo\f* yokudumisa\x + Mark. 14.26-31.\x* baphuma\x + Luka 22.39. Joha. 18.1. Mat. 26.36.\x* baya entabeni yeMihlwathi\x + 21.1.\x*.
\s Ukuxwayiswa kukaPetro
\p
\v 31 UJesu wasesithi kubo: Lina lonke lizakhubeka ngami ngalobubusuku\x + 11.6.\x*; ngoba kulotshiwe \add ukuthi\add*: Ngizatshaya umelusi, izimvu zomhlambi\x + Zek. 13.7.\x* besezihlakazeka\x + Joha. 16.32.\x*.
\v 32 Kodwa emva kokuvuswa kwami, ngizalandulela ukuya eGalili\x + 28.7,10,16. Mark. 16.7.\x*.
\v 33 Kodwa uPetro waphendula wathi kuye: Lanxa bonke bezakhubeka ngawe, mina angisoze ngikhubeke\x + Luka 22.33.\x*.
\v 34 UJesu wathi kuye: Ngiqinisile ngithi kuwe: Ngalobubusuku\x + Luka 22.34. Joha. 13.38.\x*, lingakakhali iqhude, uzangiphika kathathu\x + 26.75. Mark. 14.30.\x*.
\v 35 UPetro wathi kuye: Loba kudingeka ngife lawe, angisoze ngikuphike. Basebesitsho njalo bonke abafundi\x + Luka 22.33. Joha. 13.37.\x*.
\s EGetsemane
\p
\v 36 UJesu wasefika labo endaweni\x + Mark. 14.32-42. Luka 22.39-42,45,46.\x* ethiwa yiGetsemane, wasesithi kubafundi: Hlalani phansi lapha, ngisayakhuleka laphaya\x + Joha. 18.1.\x*.
\v 37 Wasethatha kanye laye uPetro lamadodana amabili kaZebediya\x + 4.21. Mat. 17.1.\x*, waqala ukudabuka lokukhathazeka kakhulu\x + Fil. 2.26.\x*.
\v 38 Wasesithi kubo: Umphefumulo wami udabukile kakhulu kuze kube sekufeni\x + Joha. 12.27.\x*; hlalani lapha lilinde lami\x + 26.40,41. 24.42.\x*.
\v 39 Waseqhubeka ibangana, wawa ngobuso bakhe wakhuleka wathi\x + Heb. 5.7.\x*: Baba, uba kungenzeka\x + Joha. 12.27.\x*, kakudlule kimi linkezo\x + 20.22.\x*; kodwa kungabi njengoba ngithanda mina\x + 26.42. Joha. 5.30; 6.38. Fil. 2.8.\x*, kodwa njengoba \add uthanda\add* wena\x + Mat. 6.10.\x*.
\v 40 Wasesiza kubafundi, wabafica belele\x + 26.39.\x*, wathi kuPetro: Kanti belingelinde\x + Mark. 7.18. 1 Kor. 6.5.\x* lami ihola ibenye\x + 26.40,41.24.42.\x*?
\v 41 Lindani likhuleke, ukuze lingangeni ekulingweni\x + Luka 22.40,46. Efe. 6.18. Mat. 6.13.\x*; umoya isibili uyavuma, kodwa inyama ibuthakathaka\x + Gal. 5.17. Roma 7.23.\x*.
\v 42 Wabuya wasuka ngokwesibili wakhuleka, wathi: Baba\x + 26.42. Joha. 5.30; 6.38. Fil. 2.8.\x*, uba inkezo le ingedlule kimi, ngaphandle kokuthi ngiyinathe\x + 20.22.\x*, kayenziwe intando yakho\x + Mat. 6.10.\x*.
\v 43 Wasebuya wabafica futhi belele, ngoba amehlo abo ayenzima\x + Luka 9.32.\x*.
\v 44 Wasebatshiya wahamba futhi wakhuleka ngokwesithathu, esitsho wona lawomazwi.
\v 45 Wasesiza kubafundi bakhe, wathi kubo: Qhubekani lilele, liphumule\x + 2 Tim. 4.8. Heb. 10.13.\x*; khangelani, isikhathi sesisondele, futhi iNdodana yomuntu iyanikelwa ezandleni zezoni.
\v 46 Sukumani, sihambe; khangelani, onginikelayo useduze\x + Mark. 14.35.\x*.
\s Ukubotshwa kukaJesu lokuthethwa kwecala lakhe
\p
\v 47 Kwathi esakhuluma, khangela, kwafika uJudasi, omunye wabalitshumi lambili\x + Mark. 14.43-50. Luka 22.47-53. Joha. 18.3-11.\x*, lexuku elikhulu lilaye elilezinkemba lezinduku, livela kubapristi abakhulu labadala babantu\x + 10.10. Mark. 14.43,48. Luka 22.52.\x*.
