\v 53 Kumbe ucabanga ukuthi ngingemcele uBaba yini khathesi, futhi anginike amabutho amakhulu ezingilosi\x + 4.11. 2 Kho. 6.17. Dan. 7.10.\x* edlula itshumi lambili\x + Mark. 5.9,15. Luka 8.30.\x*?
\v 54 Pho ingagcwaliseka njani imibhalo, ukuthi kumele ukuthi kube njalo\x + Isa. 53.7-10. Lilo 4.20. Mat. 26.56.26.24.\x*?
\v 55 Ngalelohola uJesu wathi emaxukwini: Liphume njengokuyamelana lomphangi\x + Joha. 10.1,8; 18.40. 2 Kor. 11.26. Mat. 21.13; 27.38,44. Luka 10.30,36.\x* yini lilezinkemba lezinduku ukuzangibamba\x + 26.55. Mark. 14.43,48. Luka 22.52.\x*? Bengihlezi insuku ngensuku\x + Luka 2.46. Joha. 8.2. Mat. 5.1. Luka 5.3.\x* ethempelini ngifundisa, kodwa kalingibambanga\x + Mark. 12.35. Luka 21.37. Joha. 7.28; 8.20. Joha. 18.20.\x*.
